00:45:58.770 --> 00:46:01.200
But what these four
children have taught

00:46:01.200 --> 00:46:03.480
me is this lesson that
I've repeated here,

00:46:03.480 --> 00:46:05.680
that we enter the world as
curious, creative people.

00:46:05.680 --> 00:46:09.060
And I now have a firm belief
that the world's biggest

00:46:09.060 --> 00:46:12.070
untapped source of
energy isn't in the wind.

00:46:12.070 --> 00:46:13.230
It isn't in the water.

00:46:13.230 --> 00:46:14.730
It isn't in the sun.

00:46:14.730 --> 00:46:16.890
It's inside our
large organizations

00:46:16.890 --> 00:46:20.430
that are filled with human
beings that were once like this

00:46:20.430 --> 00:46:22.470
that are now shackled
and constrained,

00:46:22.470 --> 00:46:24.360
not realizing their
full potential

00:46:24.360 --> 00:46:27.070
related to curiosity
and creativity.

00:46:27.070 --> 00:46:28.620
This is my life's mission.

00:46:28.620 --> 00:46:30.690
I view my job as a
parent to make sure

00:46:30.690 --> 00:46:33.690
that my children never lose
their love of learning.

00:46:33.690 --> 00:46:36.630
I view my job as an advisor
to large organizations

00:46:36.630 --> 00:46:39.150
to help leaders of these
organizations release,

00:46:39.150 --> 00:46:42.780
harness, and amplify the latent
energy that exists within.

00:46:42.780 --> 00:46:45.010
After all, as
Archimedes once said,

00:46:45.010 --> 00:46:47.550
you give me a lever long
enough and a platform on which

00:46:47.550 --> 00:46:50.160
