can move the world.

00:46:50.160 --> 00:46:53.120
The platform that you
have at your organization,

00:46:53.120 --> 00:46:56.470
the platform that people have
at many large organizations,

00:46:56.470 --> 00:46:57.531
is unbelievable.

00:46:57.531 --> 00:46:59.530
It's the sort of thing
that the startups are all

00:46:59.530 --> 00:47:01.800
fighting like crazy to create.

00:47:01.800 --> 00:47:03.930
The potential is there.

00:47:03.930 --> 00:47:05.880
I hope the ideas that
